T1  - Efficiency, technical change, and returns to scale in large US banks: Panel data evidence from an output distance function satisfying theoretical regularity
AU  - Feng, Guohua
AU  - Serletis, Apostolos
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 34
IS  - 1
